  "lines": [
    {
      "lineNumber": 1,
      "text": "Director, FBI",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 2,
      "text": "August 5, 1952",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 3,
      "text": "SAC, San Diego",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 4,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 5,
      "text": "In view of the current hysteria concerning the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "text": "so-called \"flying saucers\", I thought that the Bureau",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "text": "might be interested in the following information concern-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "ing the captioned organization.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "I am transmitting herewith certain literature con-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "cerning the captioned organization which was furnished to",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "me by [REDACTED] who operates the [REDACTED]",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "Company in San Diego and who has his office in the same",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "building housing the FBI office.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "It is of interest to note that on Friday, August 1,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "1952, at approximately 12:00 noon, [REDACTED] asked to see",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "me urgently, which I did. As a member of the captioned",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "organization, he advised me that they were having a meeting",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "at 1:00 PM the same day, inasmuch as they had been advised",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "that they had some very important information to discuss.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "He went on to relate that through the means utilized by his",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "organization (which the enclosed literature will reflect",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "borders on the occult), they were able to prognosticate",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "well in advance the recent earthquake which occurred in",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "Tehachapi, California. He advised that they have also",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "been able to obtain the following information:",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "1. That a very severe tidal wave will hit the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "Pacific Ocean sometime in the not too remote future and",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "that most of the Japanese Islands will be washed away",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "and disappear.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "2. That all fishes with scales in Japanese",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "waters will soon leave these waters for other destina-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "tions, in view of the oncoming tidal wave.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "3. That this tidal wave will wash away the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "text": "Hawaiian Islands.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "text": "4. That the West Coast of the United States will",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "text": "likewise be affected by this tidal wave.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 43,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 44,
      "text": "5. That they prognosticated the appearance of",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 45,
      "text": "a new island in the Pacific which was published in the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 46,
      "text": "newspapers within the past week.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 47,
      "status": "blank"
    },
